    <a title="Sotiris Makrygiannis" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/16896341-sotiris-makrygiannis"><img alt="Sotiris Makrygiannis" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1463503460p2/16896341.jpg" /></a>

