<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6895978-a-country-of-vast-designs"><img alt="A Country of Vast Designs: James K. Polk, the Mexican War and the Conquest of the American Continent" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1442277412l/6895978._SX98_.jpg" />
