      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/19093525-the-man-who-saved-the-union-ulysses-grant-in-war-and-peace">Quotes from The Man Who Saved...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Shiloh showed him what he could ask of his men, and indeed what he MUST ask of them.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/6751742-shiloh-showed-him-what-he-could-ask-of-his-men">3 likes</a>
            </nobr>
            <div class="clear"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;He was like a man thinking on an abstract subject all the time.&rdquo;</span>
